A 32-year-old actor and radio personality is expected to appear in the Pretoria Magistrate's Court on Tuesday, after being caught by Tshwane police allegedly driving under the influence of alcohol.He was spotted driving a Jaguar without exercising due caution during the early hours of Friday morning at the corner of Nelson Mandela and Rissik Street, Sunnyside.He was released on a R1 000 bail.Source: News24